    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
あゝ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">終</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の夕は来りぬ、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">天昏</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">てんこん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">地昏</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ちこん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にさはなる<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">不浄</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふじやう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>はもこゝに亡ぶか、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">洗礼女</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あらはれめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>――<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">河原</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かはら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">葦</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
法涙の露無量光、<lb />
新らしき<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">生命</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いのち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の慈相――<lb />
<lb />
十<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">夜</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">や</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">法会</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほうゑ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の跡さびしき、<lb />
天台の寺院の堂に、<lb />
いからしく波うつ霧や、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">仏龕</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ぶつがん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の虫ばむ音は、<lb />
悲しとも、これも自然が<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">法</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">のり</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の座へ辿る<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">足音</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あのと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ぞ、<lb />
きけ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">葦</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のさなす小琴に、<lb />
霊のうた『血汐は白し<lb />
血は白し、こや<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">敬虔</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うやまひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">古瓶</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふるがめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の封を破らず<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">時</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をまち考え<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">伏</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>して<lb />
いまぞいま『自然』に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">浸</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひた</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>す、<lb />
<lb />
白き血に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">映</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うつ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">大天</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おほあめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<lb />
白き血を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">吸</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">す</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>へや<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">大地</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おほつち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><lb />
ありとある<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">孤独</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こどく</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のものは<lb />
静寂の法に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">帰依</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きえ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>して<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">黙</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">もだ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>しつゝ白き血<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">飲</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">の</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>め』と、<lb />
きくからに身も溶けごゝち。<lb />
<lb />
見かへれば<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">喬木</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おほき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のしげみ<lb />
天台の寺院は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">闇</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">やみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に――<lb />
うなだれて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">物思</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ものおも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ひ立てる<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">己</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おの</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>が身も小河も葦も<lb />
大法の一切滅に<lb />
あゝなべて見えざる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">光輝</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かゞやき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>――<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
